metadata.name: Elephant Rock
metadata.description:
I have seen many photographs from locations throughout the world of places known as ‘Elephant Rock’, well this is the Irish version. The Irish ‘Elephant Rock’ can be found off the North Antrim coast in a small town called Ballintoy. 

Ballintoy’s picturesque Atlantic coastline has been known more recently as one of the filming locations for the popular ‘Game of Thrones’ series, but for me, the star of the show is still the ‘Elephant Rock’. 

Artist: Michael McCafferty 

Collection: Irish Seascapes 

Edition: 1/1
